    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {className: a4; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 5.65pt; margin-bottom: 5.65pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Васиятноманинг тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#2}Васиятнома тасдиқланган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни ушбу васиятномани мен – Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Васиятномани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> васият қилувчининг хоҳиш-иродасига ва Ўзбекистон Республикаси қонун ҳужжатларига асосан тасдиқладим.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Васиятномани фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Васиятномани имзолаган фуқаронинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> менинг ҳузуримда ўқиб, имзолади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Васият қилувчининг шахси аниқланди ва унинг муомалага лаёқатлилиги текширилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Шахсий мулоқот давомида унинг муомалага лаёқатсизлигига шубҳа туғилмади ва ушбу нотариал ҳаракатни амалга ошириш даврида нотариал идорада унинг муомалага лаёқатсизлиги ҳақида ҳеч қандай маълумотлар йўқ.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Реестрга </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#7}Васиятномани реестрга қайд қилинган рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сон билан қайд қилинди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Давлат божи:</span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Давлат божи миқдори </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариус <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span></p>\n</div></div>",
